{"tid":1113292,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【含多年數據】究竟點解歐聯雙英內訌，例牌係聯賽排名較低嗰隊出綫？","createTime":"2019-04-17T23:11:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T08:07:12.000Z","uid":165817,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d0264c8e50aae5a5a484354df8bec8574e8036d2","tid":1113292,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T23:11:31.000Z","msg":"2003-04<br />\n車路士(2) 淘汰 阿仙奴(1)<br />\n<br />\n2004-05<br />\n利物浦(5) 淘汰 車路士(1)<br />\n<br />\n2006-07<br />\n利物浦(3) 淘汰 車路士(2)<br />\n<br />\n2007-08<br />\n利物浦(4) 淘汰 阿仙奴(3)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">車路士(2) 淘汰 利物浦(4)<br />\n曼聯(1) 淘汰 車路士(2)</span><br />\n<br />\n2008-09<br />\n車路士(3) 淘汰 利物浦(2)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">曼聯(1) 淘汰 阿仙奴(4)</span><br />\n<br />\n2010-11<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">曼聯(1) 淘汰 車路士(2)</span><br />\n<br />\n2017-18<br />\n利物浦(3) 淘汰 曼城(1)<br />\n<br />\n2018-19<br />\n熱刺(3/4) 淘汰 曼城(1/2)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廿一世紀歐聯總共出現過11次英超內訌，其中有7次，都係由聯賽排名較低嗰隊出綫 (紅字嗰四場係例外)。<br />\n<br />\n當中不敗阿仙奴、摩一車路士、百分曼城呢三支英超史上最經典、實力最雄厚嘅冠軍球隊，都係爆冷輸俾同國對手而出局。<br />\n<br />\n同埋值得留意，出局嗰隊唔止喺聯賽排名上高過對手，英超賽場直接對碰都普遍係佔優，但出到歐洲就反而例牌唔夠踢。<br />\n<br />\n其實雖然話就話係歐聯，但兩隊踢落嘅風格都係一樣，唔會話因為喺歐聯賽場，就放棄哂平時喺英超嗰種踢法。唯一不同只係兩回合制，但究竟點解會有咁大影響？"},{"pid":"7e0d2c1bde84bb0efbb8fad6a416716c32f1eacd","tid":1113292,"uid":165817,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T23:14:52.000Z","msg":"更正少少 上季利物浦應該係第4"},{"pid":"bf86e74ca04447124618d55ae3f00704890f2dab","tid":1113292,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T01:53:59.000Z","msg":"sample 太細，況且7/11 都係六成三，好難叫例牌喎"},{"pid":"6656fa63ad499bedd5582d2f7c907f3cd4cc50dd","tid":1113292,"uid":125992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf86e74ca04447124618d55ae3f00704890f2dab","tid":1113292,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T01:53:59.000Z","msg":"sample 太細，況且7/11 都係六成三，好難叫例牌喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T02:16:51.000Z","msg":"起碼七成準先拎出黎啦，仲以為樓主有驚人發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b89cb42a571eeba6503fd4be297d838ecdbba03","tid":1113292,"uid":9958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T02:37:17.000Z","msg":"何謂例牌"},{"pid":"9294573fa60d1eef05e91d070e0d014a86cbb7e9","tid":1113292,"uid":164730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T04:51:00.000Z","msg":"曼連係例外 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c373c8807d3361e58d9f09e68ad620689fa3ed","tid":1113292,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6656fa63ad499bedd5582d2f7c907f3cd4cc50dd","tid":1113292,"uid":125992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf86e74ca04447124618d55ae3f00704890f2dab","tid":1113292,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T01:53:59.000Z","msg":"sample 太細，況且7/11 都係六成三，好難叫例牌喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T02:16:51.000Z","msg":"起碼七成準先拎出黎啦，仲以為樓主有驚人發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T08:00:27.000Z","msg":"不過其實嗰四次有三次都係神級嘅費格遜<br />\n跟住就只有格蘭一個晉到級<br />\n都證明好多領隊都有呢個問題"},{"pid":"4a5d47f535828a7c3bb495254dbb260bb87a1604","tid":1113292,"uid":218659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T08:07:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}